Based on the numerical kinetic model and observations of the ENA fluxes from IHS by the IBEX-Hi instrument, Baliukin et al. (2022) characterized the pickup proton distribution and provided estimations on the properties of the energetic pickup proton population downstream of the TS. They have performed the parametric study by varying ξ\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
