PUIs in the outer heliosphere have the dominant pressure (McComas et al. 2017) and are not equilibrated with the background thermal plasma (Zank et al. 2014). The thermal gas temperature (Richardson et al. 2008) and PUI temperature (Zank et al. 2010) upstream of the TS are about 0.2×106\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
