				\begin{document}$D_{pp}$\end{document}, the momentum diffusion equation has a steady-state solution of the distribution function for accelerated particles of the form ∝p−3\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym}
